,["$","td",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"REJECTED"}]," by default"]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Why license-first, not relevance-first"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["The only outcome we refuse is shipping an image we can't justify. A marginally-better photo under an unknown license is worthless to a pipeline that needs to ship without human review. Relevance ties are easy to break; provenance is not. When you want relevance-first, you're usually in a speculative exploration flow — use"," ",["$","code",null,{"children":"licensePolicy: \"prefer-safe\""}]," to keep unsafe results but push them to the back."]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Why UNKNOWN is rejected"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"A missing license is not \"probably fine\". Most of the web is all-rights-reserved by default under the Berne Convention. If we guessed \"safe\" we'd ship infringing images. Better: we surface structured coverage gaps so the caller can make an explicit call — pay for a press photo, email the photographer, or drop the feature."}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Attribution"}],["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","code",null,{"children":"buildAttribution()"}]," produces a single human-readable string, kept as a string rather than structured markup so callers can render it inline in a tooltip, a footer, or a dedicated credits page."]}],["$","blockquote",null,{"children":"\"Drake at OVO Fest 2019\" by Jane Photog (Wikimedia Commons), licensed CC BY-SA 4.0"}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Confidence score"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Each candidate carries a ",["$","code",null,{"children":"confidence"}]," in [0, 1]:"]}],["$","ul",null,{"children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"0.95"}]," — structured license metadata from an authoritative API"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"0.85"}]," — platform-owned license (Unsplash, Pexels, Pixabay)"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"0.6–0.8"}]," — heuristics + coercion"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"≤ 0.4"}]," — host-based guess only"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"0"}]," — no evidence"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Any candidate with ",["$","code",null,{"children":"confidence < 0.5"}]," should be re-verified before shipping even if its tag is \"safe\"."]}],["$","h2",null,{"children":"Browser-sourced images"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["Images retrieved via the opt-in browser fallback are always tagged"," ","$L11",", carry a source-URL sidecar, and require an explicit per-call opt-in flag. We do not attempt to classify their license; that is the caller's responsibility."]}]]}],null,"$L12"]}]
